#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Today's topic is about praise.\n"
"\n"
"Praise is a powerful parenting skill.\n"
"\n"
"If we praise our teens when they do something well, we will see them do more and more positive things!"
msgstr ""
"Kipindi cha leo ni kuhusu Kusifia.\n"
"\n"
"Kusifia ni ujuzi wenye nguvu katika malezi.\n"
"\n"
"Kama tutawasifia vijana wetu wanapofanya jambo vizuri, tutawaona wakifanya mambo mazuri zaidi na zaidi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "How will praise help you and your family? Tap play to find out!"
msgstr "Jinsi gani kusifia itasakusaidia na familia yako? Gusa cheza ili kujua!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Greetings everyone.\n"
"\n"
"Our topic today is about praise.\n"
"\n"
"It is good to praise our children when they've done good because when we do that, they will do more of that good behavior we want to see.\n"
"\n"
"And let's not forget to praise ourselves when we do good!"
msgstr ""
"Habari zenu?\n"
"\n"
"Kipindi chetu ya leo inahusu kusifia.\n"
"\n"
"Ni vizuri kuwasifia watoto wetu wanapofanya vizuri kwa sababu tunapofanya hivyo, watazidi kuifanya tabia nzuri tunayotaka kuiona.\n"
"\n"
"Na tusisahau pia kujisifia sisi wenyewe tunapofanya mazuri!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Praise is an easy way to build your teen‚Äôs confidence and strengthen your connection. It really works!"
msgstr "Kusifia ni njia rahisi kujenga kujiamini kwa kijana wako na kuimarisha uhusiano wenu. Inafanya kazi kweli!"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_female_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Praise works, but it‚Äôs not always easy. Hear how @data.characters.media_female_2.name started using it at home"
msgstr "Kusifia kunafanya kazi, lakini siyo rahisi daima. Sikiliza jinsi @data.characters.media_female_2.name alivyoanza kuitumia nyumbani"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"When we learnt about this praising thing I thought, ‚ÄúWe were never praised for things as teenagers, so why should we start now?‚Äù But I got interested when I learnt what the benefits of praising could be.\n"
"\n"
"Right after the weekly workshop, I noticed my teen doing what they do every day: washing the dishes. And I said ‚ÄúThank you for washing the dishes, my girl, it really makes me happy that you are helping out.‚Äù My teen was smiling and she even came to give me a hug, which she never does.\n"
"\n"
"This praising business is hard. I still forget sometimes or give praise at the same time as criticism. But praising really makes a difference. I never thought that a simple praise could make such a change in a person!"
msgstr ""
"Tulipojifunza kuhusu jambo hili la kusifu nilifikiri, ‚ÄúHatukusifiwa kamwe kwa mambo tukiwa vijana, kwa hivyo kwa nini tuanze sasa?‚Äù Lakini nilipendezwa nilipojifunza faida za kusifu zingeweza kuwa nini.\n"
"\n"
"Mara tu baada ya warsha ya kila wiki, niliona kijana wangu akifanya kile anachofanya kila siku: kuosha vyombo. Na nikasema, \"Asante kwa kuosha vyombo, msichana wangu, inanifurahisha sana kwamba unasaidia.\" Kijana wangu alikuwa akitabasamu na hata alikuja kunikumbatia, jambo ambalo huwa hafanyi.\n"
"\n"
"Biashara hii ya kusifu ni ngumu. Bado ninasahau wakati mwingine au kutoa sifa wakati huo huo kama ukosoaji. Lakini kusifu kunafanya tofauti. Sikuwahi kufikiria kwamba sifa rahisi inaweza kufanya mabadiliko hayo kwa mtu!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Let‚Äôs reflect on our own experience with praise."
msgstr "Ebu tujikumbushe kwenye uzoefu wetu wa kusifia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Think about the last time someone thanked you, or said you did something great.\n"
"\n"
"How did it make you feel?"
msgstr ""
"Fikiria kuhusu mara ya mwisho mtu alipokushukuru, au alipokuambia umefanya kitu fulani kizuri sana.\n"
"\n"
"Ilikufanya ujisikieje?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay"
msgstr "Sawa"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "We sometimes have to get used to being praised and praising others. That‚Äôs okay."
msgstr "Sisi wakati mwingine tunatakiwa kuzoea kusifiwa na kusifia wengine. Hiyo ni sawa."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Happy"
msgstr "Furaha"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Being praised often makes us feel happy."
msgstr "Hiyo ni nzuri Sana! Kusifia mara kwa mara hutufanya kujihisi wenye furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Proud"
msgstr "Kujivunia"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That‚Äôs great! Being praised often makes us feel proud."
msgstr "Hiyo ni nzuri Sana! Kusifia mara kwa mara hutufanya kujihisi wenye furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Parents usually do not get thanked or praised enough.\n"
"\n"
"How does it make you feel when nobody says \"thank you\"?"
msgstr ""
"Mara nyingi Wazazi hawapewi shukrani au kusifia vya kutosha.\n"
"\n"
"Unajisikiaje pale ambapo hakuna mtu anakamia \"asante\"?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Sad"
msgstr "Huzuni"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Angry"
msgstr "Hasira"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Tired"
msgstr "Kuchoka"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Your teen can feel this way too. That's what makes this week's parenting tool simple but important: Praise them for what they do right."
msgstr "Kijana wako anaweza pia kujisikia hivyo. Hicho ndicho kinachofanya nyenzo ya malezi ya wiki hii iwe rahisi lakini muhimu: Msifie anapofanya vizuri."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Just like we feel better when praised, teens do too. Let‚Äôs look at a simple example with @data.characters.f1_father.name and his son, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name."
msgstr "Kama ambavyo tunajisikia vizuri tunapo pongezwa, na kwa vijana uwa hivyo pia.Hebu tuangalie mfano rahisi wa @data.characters.f1_father.name na kijana wake, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thank you for doing the dishes, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. It's a big help!"
msgstr "Asante kwa kuosha vyombo, @data.characters.f1_son_18.name. Umesaidia sana!"

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.role_name,
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "@data.characters.f1_father.role_name, I hate doing the dishes every day. It is women‚Äôs work! @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name or @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name should be doing them. Even my book at school only shows women doing the dishes."
msgstr "@data.characters.f1_father.role_name, Nachukia kuosha vyombo kila siku. Nikazi za watoto wakike! @data.characters.f1_mother.role_name au @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name ndo wanatakiwa kuwa wanaviosha. Hata kitabu changu cha shule kinaonyesha wanawake pekee ndio wanao osha vyomba."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_mother_role.name
#.      @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It is not women‚Äôs work. @data.characters.f1_mother_role.name and @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name  are busy at work and school all day as well. We all need to play our part at home too."
msgstr "Sio kazi za watoto wakike pekee.@data.characters.f1_mother_role.name na @data.characters.f1_daughter_16.name na wao wanakua bize na majukumu ya kazini na shuleni siku nzima. Wote kwa pamoja tunatakiwa kushiriki majukumu ya nyumbani pia."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Okay, fine."
msgstr "Haya, saw."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I know it's hard to understand, but it's important that we all work together. Doing this kind of work will help you become an independent and responsible man when you have your own family. \n"
"\n"
"I am proud of you for doing your part. Here, let me help you dry the dishes."
msgstr ""
"Najua ni ngumu kuelewa, lakini ni muhimu wote kwa pamoja kufanya kazi. kufanya kazi za namna hii itakusaidia wewe kuwa mwanaume muwajibikaji na anayejitegemea utakapokuja kuwa na familia yako mwenyewe.\n"
"\n"
"Ninajivunia wewe kwa kufanya sehemu yako. Haya, nikupe msaada kukausha vyombo."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_father.role_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Thanks for helping me @data.characters.f1_father.role_name."
msgstr "Asante kwa kunisaidia @data.characters.f1_father.role_name."

#. type=data_list
#. The following strings should not be translated: 
#.      @data.characters.f1_father.name‚Äôs
#.      @data.characters.f1_son_18.name?
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Why did @data.characters.f1_father.name‚Äôs praise help @data.characters.f1_son_18.name?"
msgstr "Kwanini pongezi za@data.characters.f1_father.name zilimsaidia@data.characters.f1_son_18.name?"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It made @data.characters.f1_son_18.name feel seen and appreciated"
msgstr "Ilimfanya @data.characters.f1_son_18.name kujihisi mwenye kuonekana na kukubalika"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It helped @data.characters.f1_son_18.name feel respected and more willing to help again"
msgstr "Ilimsaidia@data.characters.f1_son_18.name kujihisi kuheshiwa na kumuongezea shahuku ya kusaidia tena"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.f1_son_18.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It made @data.characters.f1_son_18.name feel more connected to his father"
msgstr "Ilimafanya @data.characters.f1_son_18.name kujihisi yupo karibu sana na baba yake"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Exactly! Praising boys and girls encourages them to both play their part at home. It teaches fairness, life skills, and helps build a more respectful family."
msgstr "Sahihi kabisa! kuwapongeza watoto wakike na wakiume inawahasisha kushiriki shughuli za nyumbani. inawafundisha usawa, stadi za maisha na inasaidia kujenga familia yenye heshima."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"Here are some skills to help you praise your teens.\n"
"You can also praise other adults in your household, too. Notice how they respond!"
msgstr ""
"Huu hapa ni baadhi ya ujuzi wa kukusaidia kusifia vijana wako.\n"
"Unaweza pia kusifia watu wazima nyumbani kwako, vilevile. Gundua jins wanavyoitikia!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SEE IT"
msgstr "ONA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Look for anything your teen does that is helpful or good and praise them for it. They may not show it, but you will see them doing that good thing again. It will also reassure them that you notice and care."
msgstr "Tafuta kitu chochote anachofanya kijana wako kwa ajili ya kusaidia au kilicho kizuri na umsifie kwa kitu hicho. Anaweza asioneshe furaha yake, lakini utamwona akifanya tena kitu hicho kizuri. Pia itamthibitishia kuwa unatambua anachokifanya na unajali."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "SAY IT"
msgstr "SEMA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Be enthusiastic ‚Äì really mean it when you say it!"
msgstr "Onyesha shauku ‚Äì unaposema jambo, liseme kwa moyo wa dhati!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "REPEAT IT"
msgstr "RUDIA"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Try to find something to thank your teens for every day. Even something really small."
msgstr "Jaribu kutafuta jambo la kuwa unawapongeza nalo vijana wako kila siku. hata kama likiwa jambo dogo sana."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "More tips"
msgstr "Vidokezo zaidi"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, both boys and girls respond best to positive attention. When they feel noticed and appreciated at home, they are less likely to take risks to earn approval from others."
msgstr "Kumbuka wasichana na wavulana wote hujibu vyema wanapopokea mapokeo chanya. Wanapojihisi kutambulika na kukubalika nyumbani, inapunguza uwezekano wa kujaribu kutafuta kukubalika na watu wengine."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "It can be hard to think of reasons to praise your teen! Here are some ideas from other parents:"
msgstr "Wakati mwingine ni vigumu kufikiria kitu gani cha kumsifia kijana wako! Haya ni mawazo kutoka kwa wazazi wengine:"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"**Thank you for...**\n"
"- Being kind to someone\n"
"- Cleaning your room\n"
"- Joining a family meal\n"
"- Greeting other family members\n"
"- Looking after your siblings\n"
"- Coming home on time\n"
"- Showing thoughtfulness\n"
"- Saying 'please' or 'thank you'\n"
"- Going to school on time\n"
"- Doing chores or schoolwork"
msgstr ""
"**Asante kwa...**\n"
"- Kuwa mkarimu kwa mtu fulani\n"
"- Kusafisha chumba chako\n"
"- Kujiunga katika chakula cha familia\n"
"- Kusalimia wanafamilia wengine\n"
"- Kuwaangalia wadogo zako\n"
"- Kurudi nyumbani kwa wakati\n"
"- Kuonyesha unafikiria\n"
"- Kusema ‚Äútafadhali‚Äù au ‚Äúasante‚Äù\n"
"- Kwenda shule kwa wakati\n"
"- Kufanya kazi za nyumbani au kazi za shule"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "This week‚Äôs home activity is to praise your teen once a day. It only takes a few seconds."
msgstr "Shughuli ya nyumbani kwa wiki hii itakuwa kuwapongeza vijana wako walau mara moja kwa siku. inachukua sekunde chache tu."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Can you praise your teen once a day this week?"
msgstr "Unaweza kumsifia kijana wako mara moja kwa siku kwa wiki hii?"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Yes"
msgstr "Ndiyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's great! Parents who practise praise at home get better results!"
msgstr "Hiyo ni nzuri Sana! Wazazi wanaofanya zoezi la kusifia nyumbani wanapata Matokeo mazuri zaidi!"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "I think so"
msgstr "Nafikiri hivyo"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "You can do it! Try praising your teen for something simple at first, like looking after their siblings or going to school."
msgstr "Unaweza kufanya! Jaribu kumsifia kijana wako kwa kitu rahisi mwanzoni, kwa kuwaangalia wdago zake a kwa kwenda shule."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "No"
msgstr "Hapana"

#. type=data_list
#. The string @global.app_name. should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "That's okay. With time, giving praise will become easier. Try to praise yourself for something first, like \"Good job using @global.app_name. It shows you care.\""
msgstr "Hiyo ni sawa. Baada ya muda, kusifia itakuwa rahisi zaidi. Jaribu kujisifia mwenyewe kwa kitu flani kwanza, kama \"Kazi nzuri @global.app_name. Huonesha unajari\"."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Remember, praise is a powerful tool. The more attention you give to positive behaviour, the more positive behaviour you will see."
msgstr "Kumbuka, kusifia ni nyenzo yenye nguvu. Kadri unavyoweka umakini zaidi kwenye tabia chanya, ndivyo utakavyoona zaidi tabia chanya."

#. type=data_list
#. The string @data.characters.media_daughter_2.name should not be translated.
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Hear from @data.characters.media_daughter_2.name on how it feels to get praise from her mother"
msgstr "Sikia kutoka @data.characters.media_daughter_2.name jinsi anavyojisikia aliposifiwa na mama yake"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid ""
"I was grateful when my mother learned about praise.\n"
"\n"
"Before the workshop, she mostly noticed when I did something wrong. She would shout and sometimes hit me.\n"
"\n"
"But after the workshop, she began praising me for small things ‚Äî even things she never noticed before, like my good maths grades. At first I thought, ‚ÄòWhat is going on?‚Äô But she kept doing it. I liked it, so I started doing more good things.\n"
"\n"
"It feels good that my mother now sees the good in me, not only the bad.\n"
"\n"
"One day during one-on-one time, I told her, ‚ÄòThank you, Mama, for saying something nice when I do things well, not only when I do things wrong.‚Äô It made both of us very happy."
msgstr ""
"Nilishukuru sana mama yangu alipojifunza kupongeza\n"
"\n"
"Kabla ya mafunzo, alipotambua nimefanya kosa, alikuwa anaweza kunifokea na mara nyingine kunipiga.\n"
"\n"
"Lakini baada ya mafunzo, alianza kunipongeza hata kwa jambo dogo- hata mambo ambayo hakuwa ameyatambua kabla, mfano maksi nzuri za hesabu nilizozipata. mara ya kwanza nilijiuliza, nini kinaendelea? lakini aliendelea kufanya hivyo. Nilipenda na nilianza kufanya vitu vizuri zaidi.\n"
"\n"
"Ni jambo jema kwamba kwa sasa mama yangu anayaona mema ndani yangu, na sio mabaya pekee\n"
"\n"
"Siku moja tulipokuwa wawili, nilimwambia, ‚ÄòAsante mama, kwa kuniongelea vizuri ninapofanya vitu vizuri, na sio ninapokosea tu.‚Äô Inatufanya wote kwa pamoja tuwe wenye furaha."

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Well done for taking time for yourself today. üéâ"
msgstr "Hongera kwa kujipa muda wewe mwenyewe leoüéâ"

#. type=data_list
msgctxt "data_list"
msgid "Here is a short video to help you slow down before you go"
msgstr "Hii hapa video fupi ya kukusaidia kupunguza kasi (ya shughuli) kabla ya kuondoka"

